title: Volodymyr Zayarnyi
text:
Volodymyr Anatoliyovych Zayarnyi (; ; born 25 November 1970) is a <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and a former player.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Soviet%20Top%20League">Soviet Top League</a> in 1988 for <a href="FC%20Chornomorets%20Odessa">FC Chornomorets Odessa</a>.
